ui-info-help:
Can be of type <i>featuredUserSearches</i>, <i>Comments</i> or <i>search</i>. If search, define title and parameters <pre>{
    "type": "search",
    "title": "lastRecords",
    "active": true,
    "params": {
      "isTemplate": "n",
      "sortBy": "createDate",
      "sortOrder": "desc",
      "from": 1,
      "to": 12
    }
  }</pre>. And define which one is the active panel on page load.
